long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a very convenient plugin to batch download images and prompts from the midjourney channel in discord. After installing the plugin you can easily download your favorite images and prompts in just 3 steps as follows:

1, Go to any midjourney channel
2, Click on the blank space of your favorite content
3, Download

Wait for a while, it will generate a zip package containing pictures and prompts, which greatly saves time!
